WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.340 --> 00:00:02.810
Finding an answer to,
which of these questions,

00:00:02.810 --> 00:00:06.340
would require a traditional
controlled clinical trial?

00:00:07.640 --> 00:00:11.290
A manufacturer wants to know
what to charge for a new drug.

00:00:11.290 --> 00:00:15.300
A manufacturer wants to know if
it's worth developing a new drug.

00:00:15.300 --> 00:00:19.710
A manufacturer needs to prove their new
drug works better than existing drugs.

00:00:19.710 --> 00:00:20.280
Or, none of these.

